    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable paint chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery shows some wear and there is a faint lingering odor. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may require a tune-up soon as the idle is slightly rough. It\u2019s a reliable point-A-to-point-B vehicle for someone willing to put in a little cosmetic work.",
