    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration fans! This car is the perfect canvas for your next big project. While it's currently in poor condition and needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity to bring a vehicle back to life or serve as a valuable source for parts. Grab this budget-friendly challenge today!",
