      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in pristine, showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and preserved with uncompromising attention to detail, it represents the pinnacle of its class. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber and aesthetic integrity.",
