    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty to believe it\u2014it's in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready condition! I've babied this car since day one, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. It drives like a dream and is completely spotless inside and out. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis exhibits zero fatigue, with the rear subframe structurally reinforced and the double-VANOS system meticulously serviced for optimal variable valve timing. Suspension dynamics remain sharp via factory-spec MacPherson struts and multi-link rear geometry. This vehicle maintains its factory cross-drilled rotors and M-Variable differential lock, ensuring peerless mechanical integrity and a pure longitudinal driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. Flawless exterior and interior. Mechanically perfect. Low mileage. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-standard vehicle that defines the term 'mint condition.' This car has been pampered since day one, stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed to maintain its mirror-like, factory-original paint. There are absolutely no imperfections, dings, or mechanical issues to speak of. The cabin is a time capsule, featuring supple, unmarked leather seating, pristine carpeting, and a dashboard that remains untouched by sun or wear. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting every fluid change and inspection performed by master technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved piece of engineering, complete with all original keys, manuals, and window stickers. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a rare chance to own a masterpiece in its prime.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
